# 🎯 Trivia Game App
A fun and engaging AI-powered trivia game that challenges your knowledge 
across a variety of categories — built entirely with no-code AI tools.

## 🎯 Who It's For
Anyone who loves trivia, learning through play, and fun interactive experiences — 
great for individuals, teams, and events.

## ✨ Features
- Interactive trivia questions across multiple categories
- Clean, engaging game interface
- Fast and responsive gameplay experience
- Built with no-code AI — no coding required

